      "content": "i mean i hear you but i already take like 3mg of melatonin and i've been on the ambien for a bit now. it feels like they are totally different things so i didnt think it would be that bad. if i just take them at the same time it shouldn't really interfere with anything right? it's not like they're the same drug or anything.",
